channel.title: No one can log on my server,(Pics) I have cookies :\?
channel.description:
EDIT: Thread from yesterday, posting again because it still doesn't work
I have done everything other people have said and I've asked my friends to log on and they can't. I have 43594 port open on my fire wall, fire wall disabled, 43594 default port on my source and using hiyascape v1. Compiler works fine, restarter works fine, and I can log onto the server myself. Very frustrated about this...Can someone help me out?

I've changed my ip but I don't think that is the problem. I also have linksys so I can auto get a new ip.
